# DevOps 平台 Lessons Learned Log

> **说明**：本文件由 AI 自动维护，按时间倒序记录实战中发现的隐蔽风险与排障结论。
> **【强制更新规范】**
> 1. **单一主表原则**：所有新增经验必须**倒序**统一追加到下方的 Markdown 主表格中。**绝对严禁**在主表格之外另起任何零散的 `列表`、`次级小表格` 或 `### 分割的小标题`。
> 2. **记录门槛**：不记成功的流水账，只记录由于框架机制、脏数据或跨端约束导致的非直觉类障碍。
> 3. **字段约定**：The Defense 栏必须使用粗体加粗一句话结论，随后跟上落地措施。

| Timestamp | Domain | Phenomenon | Root Cause | Universal Rule (The Defense) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| 2026-04-23 | Security/Tools | detect-secrets 报 FileNotFoundError: git | 在容器内运行 detect-secrets 失败，因为轻量级生产/测试镜像中未安装 git 工具链。 | **左移工具宿主隔离律 (Shift-Left Host Isolation)**: 强依赖工程本地元数据（如 `.git` 树）的静态扫描工具（detect-secrets, pre-commit）必须在宿主机通过 `uv run` 执行，严禁强行下沉到生产容器栈内运行。 |
| 2026-04-23 | Security/Tools | safety 输出无效 JSON 导致脚本崩溃 | `safety check --json` 在输出顶部强行打印了一段纯文本的 Deprecation Warning，导致整体输出不再是合法 JSON。 | **CLI 纯净提取防御 (CLI JSON Defend)**: 严禁盲目信任外部 CLI 工具的 `--json` 标志。必须使用正则表达式 `re.search(r'\{.*\}', text, re.DOTALL)` 对输出流进行硬提取，以屏蔽各种弃用警告或调试前缀。 |
| 2026-04-20 | Plugin/Nexus | `NotNullViolation` in `nexus_components` (repository) | `session.add(obj)` followed by `save_to_staging` triggered a flush via `begin_nested()`. Since the object was in the session but non-nullable fields weren't set yet, the the automatic flush failed. | **非空约束前置赋值律 (Pre-flush Assignment Rule)**: 1. 严禁在设置完所有 `NOT NULL` 字段前将对象加入 `session` 或触发任何可能导致 `flush` 的操作（如 `begin_nested`）。2. 必须在构造函数中完成所有必填项初始化。 |
| 2026-04-20 | Plugin/Nexus | Missing `repository` field in component API items | Nexus API `list_components` items may lack the `repository` field in some versions, causing `KeyError` or `NotNullViolation`. | **源端映射冗余性原则 (Source ID Redundancy)**: 1. 批量保存方法必须显式接收 `repository` 名作为兜底。2. 严禁仅依赖 API 原始 Payload 中的字段进行核心实体对齐，必须穿透任务上下文中的环境信息。 |
| 2026-04-20 | Plugin/Sonar | Transactional Ghosting (Missing commits) | Worker logged success but database counts remained zero due to a missing `session.commit()` in the task processing loop. | **显式事务落盘律 (Explicit Transaction Commit)**: 插件 Worker 必须在 `process_task` 完成所有核心入库逻辑后执行显式 `session.commit()`。严禁仅依赖 `session.close()` 或 `flush()` 进行静默持久化。 |
| 2026-04-20 | Plugin/Sonar | SonarQube Project Discovery 403 (Forbidden) | Default Scan Token used in `.env` only has analysis upload rights, lacking project listing/search permissions. | **API 权限最小非对等审计 (API Scope Audit)**: 1. 采集插件所需的 Token 必须具备“资产发现”集权限（如 Administrator/User Token）。2. 在大规模资产同步前，必须先执行 Whoami 与 Search 探测脚本验证 Token 深度权限。 |
| 2026-04-20 | AI/Process | Handover DoD Violation (Summary vs Physical Log) | Agent prioritized generating the summary response over the mandatory physical log updates (Race condition in intent). | **交接日志物理先行律 (Log-First Handover)**: 任何宣告“交接完成”的指令，必须在同一回合包含日志文件 (session-history/lessons-learned) 的物理更新。严禁在文件落盘前输出任何带有“圆满完成”语义的总结。 |
| 2026-04-20 | dbt/Schema | Silent model breakage after field rename | Core schema refactor (e.g. `committed_date` -> `committed_at`) passed Python ingestion tests but killed 15+ dbt models and downstream metrics. | **dbt 全量建模审计律 (The Law of dbt Audit)**: 1. 凡涉及 Staging 层字段更名或重构，**必须**在交付前执行容器内 `make dbt-build`。2. 严禁仅凭数据库入库逻辑正确作为交付 DoD 标准。 |
| 2026-04-20 | Plugin/ZenTao | ZenTaoSettings attribute mismatch | Config assumed `username` but ZenTaoClient v2 requires `account`. Calling `.login()` is deprecated. | **双重协议对齐审计 (Dual Protocol Alignment)**: 1. 插件配置变量名必须与 Client 实例化参数 1:1 对齐。2. 必须废弃显式 `.login()` 调用，统一由 Client 内部实现 Token 自动刷新与连接探测。 |
| 2026-04-20 | MQ/Linux | AMQP EACCES (Erlang Cookie) | Anonymous volumes on Windows/WSL2 inheriting host permissions that block RabbitMQ internal cookie access. | **卷权限全量重置律 (Total Volume Reset)**: 环境崩溃或 MQ 启动异常时，必须执行 `docker-compose down -v` 强行抹除卷缓存并重建，严禁尝试手动修正卷内权限。 |
| 2026-04-15 | Testing/Mock | httpx.AsyncClient mocking in local scope | `httpx` locally imported in router causes `patch` to fail if targetting the module-local name. Sync methods like `json()`/`raise_for_status()` on `AsyncMock` resp fail if not properly awaited or if they aren't async. | **局部 Mock 与同步探针隔离 (Local Mock & Sync Isolation)**: 1. 局部 import httpx 时，patch 目标应为全局 `httpx.AsyncClient`。2. Mock 响应对象的同步方法（`json`, `status_code`）必须使用 `MagicMock` 或显式定义返回值，严禁混用 `AsyncMock` 导致 `coroutine not awaited` 警告。 |
| 2026-04-15 | RBAC/Schema | Import/Attribute errors when injecting SysPermission | Assumed a separate SysPermission model existed based on generic RBAC patterns while system uses Menu-Role merged model. | **显性定义权限模型协议 (Explicit RBAC Protocol)**: 1. 任何非常规建模范式（如“菜单即权限”）必须硬化写入 `contexts.md`。2. 测试中模拟权限必须通过创建 `SysMenu(perms="...")` 实例，严禁凭经验猜测模型类名。 [Codified into Skill: mdm-integrity-arbiter at 2026-04-15] |
| 2026-04-15 | Testing/Audit | Unit test failures during full coverage audit | Module-level `dependency_overrides` and `TestClient` in unit tests polluted global environment during concurrent discovery. | **测试固件局部隔离 (Fixture Local Isolation)**: 1. 涉及全局 `app` 的依赖覆盖必须下沉至 `fixture` 作用域。2. 必须在 `yield` 后执行 `.clear()`，严禁在模块顶层设置持久化的全局副作用。 [Codified into Skill: mdm-integrity-arbiter at 2026-04-15] |
| 2026-04-15 | Dash/SQL | `UndefinedColumn: column "web_url" does not exist` | SQL query directly referenced `@hybrid_property` in GitLabCommit model which has no physical persistence. | **物理列存在性物理审计 (The Law of Physical Persistence)**: 1. 编写看板 SQL 前必须通过 `grep` 或 `view_file` 确认字段是否为物理列。2. 严禁基于内存定义的逻辑属性直接进行原生的 SQL SELECT 操作。 [Codified into Skill: mdm-integrity-arbiter at 2026-04-15] |
| 2026-04-14 | AI/Audit | Blind Overwrite of Historical Logs | Using `write_to_file` with `Overwrite: true` without pre-reading context erased 100+ entries. | **禁绝盲写与强制前置取证 (No Blind Writes & Pre-read Mandatory)**: 1. 修改已存在文档（.log/.md）严禁使用 `write_to_file`。2. 必须先通过 `view_file` 建立物理快照，再使用 `replace_file_content` 进行增量合并，确保工程审计链完整。 |
| 2026-04-14 | Sonar/Arch | SonarQube N+1 query bottlenecks in transformer | Individual DB lookups for project IDs during issue batch transformation. | **内存域映射加载 (O(1) Memory Mapping)**: 1. 采集转换器 (Transformer) 必须采用“一次性批量拉取 ID 集 + 内存 Map 映射”模式。2. 严禁在批量转换循环内执行单条 SQL 查询，将同步效率由 O(N) 优化至 O(1)。 |
| 2026-04-14 | MQ/Infra | AMQP Connection Refused on Scheduler start | Scheduler started before RabbitMQ finished AMQP port (5672) binding despite Healthy status. | **MQ 指数退避重试 (MQ Backoff Retry)**: 1. 业务端连接 MQ 必须实现指数退避重试，严禁单纯依赖容器 Healthy 状态。2. 在 `mq.py` 中引入连接重试装饰器，增强环境启动韧性。 |
| 2026-04-14 | Testing | AuditPublisherThread timeout / PID Explosion | Resource starvation (MQ Alarms) triggered by test loops combined with ghost volume permissions. | **全量卷清洗与孤立审计 (Total Volume Re-sanitization)**: 1. 面对挂起超时错误，必须执行 `docker-compose down -v` 彻底清理卷权限与残留句柄。2. 必须重置 MQ 内存水线 (VM High Watermark) 防止生产者挂起并触发 PID 爆炸。 |
| 2026-04-14 | Data/SQL | PostGreSQL specific syntax errors (PRAGMA) in tests | Hardcoding SQLite commands (`PRAGMA`) in shared integration test setup without engine awareness. | **数据库方言隔离原则 (DB Dialect Isolation)**: 1. `PRAGMA` 等指令必须包裹在 `if "sqlite" in str(engine.url)` 判断中。2. 集成测试环境迁移至 PG 时，必须执行物理 Schema 取证 (`\dt`) 代替逻辑臆测表名。 |
| 2026-04-14 | AI/Agent | Rule 9: Question-word safety break triggered too late | AI prioritized "Action Impulse" over the mandatory Semantic Anchor checkpoint. | **执行态强解锁协议 (Execution Lock Protocol)**: 1. 凡包含“？”“吗”等词汇的语句，AI 必须强制挂起所有写权限并反向确认。2. 在 `AGENTS.md` 加入物理红线：违规修改代码将导致 L4 归位审核失败。 |
| 2026-04-14 | Script/Config | `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'devops_config'` | 独立脚本 (`wecom_risk_bot.py`) 仍遗留废弃的相对路径引用，且 `config.py` 的 Pydantic 中遗漏了 `NotifiersSettings` 配置树。 | **环境平移与 Pydantic 强类型防线**: 1. 所有脚本引入必须采用 `from devops_collector.config import settings`。2. 任何涉及环境变量（如 Webhook）的功能开发，**必须**先行在 `config.py` 落盘对应的 Pydantic Schema，严禁以纯字典形式绕道获取，防范生产环境配置脱节。 |
| 2026-04-13 | Plugin/ZenTao | `Instance deleted` error during product/execution sync loop | Iterating over ORM objects while performing `session.commit()` or `session.rollback()` in the same loop clears context. | **嵌套事务与对象重拉取律 (Nested Transaction & Re-query Rule)**: 1. 必须使用 `begin_nested()` 包裹循环内事务处理逻辑。 2. 循环中应迭代 ID 列表而非对象列表，并在每次迭代开始时通过 `session.get()` 重新拉取活性对象。 |
| 2026-04-13 | System/Scripts | `InvalidRequestError` when initializing mappers in standalone scratch scripts | Missing explicit imports of related plugin models (e.g. SonarProject) in isolated execution environments leads to incomplete registry. | **全模型加载强制律 (Mandatory Global Model Loading)**: 任何独立运行的辅助脚本 (Scratch/Verification) 必须首先调用 `PluginLoader.load_models()`，以确保 SQLAlchemy Registry 获取完整的跨插件关联定义，防止映射初始化失败。 |
| 2026-04-13 | Data/SQL | `UndefinedColumn` error when querying `sys_sync_logs` in diagnostic scripts | Assuming standard field names like `start_time` without verifying the model inheritance from `TimestampMixin`. | **Mixin 字段取证原则 (Mixin Field Verification)**: 在编写针对系统公共表（如日志表）的 SQL 时，必须首先核实其继承自 Mixin 的物理列名（如 `created_at`/`updated_at`），严禁凭直觉臆测。 |
| 2026-04-10 | AI/Agent | "Unexpected argument" error in Makefile after AI command modification | AI confused `uv sync` syntax with `uv export` (using `--without` incorrectly), leading to broken builds. | **指令校验取证律 (The Law of Command Validation)**: 凡涉及修改 Makefile/CI 等自动化指令，Agent **必须强制执行 `--help`** 进行取证，严禁凭关联记忆或惯性类比编写命令。同时已将此规则硬化至 `AGENTS.md` 第 70 行。 [Codified into Skill: chaos-sentinel at 2026-04-10] |
| 2026-04-10 | Dependency | Flask/Safety vulnerabilities reported in production security audit | `detect-secrets` (a dev tool) pulled in Flask as a sub-dependency, and the safety scanner checked the lockfile instead of the production manifest. | **生产依赖物理脱敏 (Production Dependency Pruning)**: 1. `requirements.txt` 必须显式通过 `uv export --no-dev --no-hashes` 构造。 2. 必须在 `contexts.md` 14.3 节建立脱敏审计红线，确保渗透类或开发类工具及其影子依赖不进入气隙生产环境。 |
| 2026-04-10 | UI/Streamlit | Streamlit page detection fails with duplicate index prefixes | Having two files like `4_Compliance_Audit.py` and `4_Quality_Monitor.py` causes Streamlit to ignore one or fail routing. | **Streamlit 页面索引唯一性 (Page Index Uniqueness)**: 必须确保 `pages/` 目录下每个文件的索引前缀 (如 `0_`, `1_`) 在全局范围内唯一，建议使用 `0_` 分配给最核心的监控页面。 |
| 2026-04-10 | Docker/Volume | Windows Docker volume sync delay for new files | Newly created files in the host (dashboard/pages/*.py) may not sync immediately or at all to the container with `.:/app` mount on Windows/WSL2. | **容器卷同步强制刷新 (Docker Volume Force Refresh)**: 1. 在 Windows 环境下新增 Python 脚本到挂载目录后，建议通过 `docker cp` 强制注入容器。 2. 必须重启该容器以触发 Streamlit 的页面重新扫描。 |
| 2026-04-10 | Data/Pandas | `AttributeError: 'float' object has no attribute 'strftime'` | SQL aggregation `max(timestamp)` might be returned as float (timestamp) in some DB adapters or Pandas versions, breaking formatted display. | **日期格式化鲁棒性 (Datetime Formatting Resilience)**: 在 UI 展示时间戳前，必须强制显式调用 `pd.to_datetime(field)`。严禁假设数据库返回的对象直接支持 `.strftime()` 方法。 |
| 2026-04-10 | Audit/Infra | Audit logs delayed visibility in integration tests after async refactor | Audit writes are now moved to a background thread with batching (timeout=3s), meaning they aren't available instantly after a service call in tests. | **异步审计可见性防御 (Async Audit Visibility)**: 集成测试中验证审计日志时，必须引入 `retry(timeout=5)` 或 `time.sleep(3)` 轮询机制，或在测试环境中强制将 `batch_size` 设为 1。 |
| 2026-04-10 | RabbitMQ/Batch | `basic_ack` must use correct channel context in batch callbacks | Pika's BlockingConnection does not support multi-threading well; the batch consumer thread must manage its own connection and channel. | **MQ 消费者线程隔离权 (Consumer Thread Isolation)**: 任何耗时的批量处理或独占线程消费者必须持有独立的 MessageQueue 实例（即独立的 Connection），严禁跨线程共用 BlockingConnection 句柄。 |
| 2026-04-09 | dbt/SQL | `invalid input syntax for numeric` for quoted JSONB | Raw data parsed from JSONB often contains physical quotes (e.g., `"123.4"`) which breaks native PG casting. | **防御性 JSONB 提取规范 (Defensive JSONB)**: All extractions from JSONB **MUST** use `nullif(trim(both '"' from field), '')` before casting. This is the ultimate isolation layer against non-standard upstream serialization. |
| 2026-04-09 | Plugin/ZenTao | `dbt build` crash with `invalid input syntax for type timestamp: "0000-00-00 00:00:00"` | ZenTao uses zero-date strings to represent NULL, which directly crashes PostgreSQL's `::timestamp` cast. | **禅道零日期拦截律 (Zero-Date Attack Defense)**: Any timestamp parsing for ZenTao **MUST** filter zero-date strings via dual `nullif`. Format: `nullif(nullif(field, ''), '0000-00-00 00:00:00')::timestamp`. |
| 2026-04-09 | MDM/SCD2 | Historic snapshots lost; impossible to track user/org changes over time | Staging models used `where is_current = true`, erasing the historical data at the ingestion layer. | **Staging 1:1 物理镜像原则 (Staging Purity Redline)**: NEVER filter business status (like `is_current`) in the staging layer! Staging must remain a 1:1 physical mirror to support SCD Type 2 historical lineage. |
| 2026-04-09 | QA/Chaos | Resilience logic (e.g. AuditLog fallback) not triggered in standard tests | Unit/Integration tests fail to simulate real-world physical starvation (DB pool exhaustion or network cuts), leading to 'dead' defensive code. | **混沌拨测常态化 (Chaos Injection as CI)**: Use `Chaos Sentinel` to actively inject physical faults (e.g., locking the DB pool) to verify resilience reporting and fallback triggers in a simulated production environment. |
| 2026-04-08 | Plugin/GitLab | Connecting to GitLab or syncing large projects returns 404 or SSL Timeout | Specific project IDs (like 1) may not exist on private instances, and high-concurrency/large data transfers can hit SSL protocol violations (`UNEXPECTED_EOF`). | **GitLab 鉴权与连通性拨测规范 (GitLab Auth & Connectivity Probe)**: 1. **鉴权验证优先**：验证 Token 时优先调用 `/version` 或 `/user` 接口，而非随机 Project ID。 2. **SSL 容错与重试**：对内网 GitLab 需设置 `verify_ssl=False` 并通过 `urllib3.disable_warnings` 消除日志噪声，Worker 必须具备指数退避重试逻辑。 |
| 2026-04-08 | Plugin/ZenTao | Discovery script crashes with AttributeError: 'ZenTaoSettings' object has no attribute 'username' | The Pydantic model for ZenTao settings used `account` instead of `username`, causing a field mismatch in the discovery logic. | **配置模型字段一致性 (Settings Field Alignment)**: 脚本中访问 `settings` 必须严格对齐 `config.py` 中的 Pydantic 定义。ZenTao 插件统一使用 `account/password` 术语，严禁在脚本中臆测为 `username`。 |
| 2026-04-08 | System/Scripts | Running standalone scripts from subdirectories leads to ModuleNotFoundError | Python's `sys.path` does not automatically include the project root when executing scripts directly (e.g., `python scripts/xxx.py`). | **脚本运行路径注入 (Script Path Injection)**: 为确保脚本在 Docker/Local 均能正确加载总包，脚本头部**必须**包含 `sys.path.append(os.getcwd())`，或始终通过 `python -m` 模式运行。 |
| 2026-04-08 | Database/Session | Scripts fail with ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'devops_collector.models.database' | `SessionLocal` isn't always exported from a consistent module; some parts use shared config engines while others use isolated sessions. | **脚本数据库会话模式 (Standalone Script DB Sessioning)**: 独立脚本建议通过 `create_engine(settings.database.uri)` 自行构造 `sessionmaker`，而非依赖全局 `SessionLocal` 变量，以提高脚本的容器内运行韧性。 |
| 2026-04-03 | Arch/Refactor | 集成测试 Collection 阶段报 `partially initialized module (most likely due to a circular import)` 及 `ModuleNotFoundError` | 在模块迁移和依赖规范化（uv）期间，`worker/transformer/client` 间的绝对路径引用与双重自注册引发环形锁死，且由于导入了错误模块路径的 `logger` 引发血案。 | **消除环形导入的解耦规范 (Circular Import Evasion)**：1. 同一包内的横向子模块间（如 Client/Worker/Transformer）必须使用相对导入 (`from .client import ...`)，在入口文件再统一暴露给外部，切忌滥用完整绝对路径互相引用。2. 插件级的 `register` 动作必须统一收拢在 `__init__.py` 等包级别入口，严禁各子模块在其底部“抢跑”级别的多头注册。 |
| 2026-04-03 | QA/Testing | 以 `us-native` 提速后，长期的 `make verify` 集成测试在半途静默死锁 (长达几分钟毫无输出) | 集成测试采用的是原生内存 SQLite，当测试执行速度呈指数级加快时，数据库连接释放未及时完成便触发新一张表的建立或级联写入，触发外键冲突造成的资源永久死锁无抛错。 | **挂起探测防呆 (Hanging Deadlock Breaker)**：面对无错误直接静默挂起的测试，首先考虑 SQLite/MemoryDB 资源隔离或竞态锁问题，这在提速的新技术栈下为高发风险。测试框架必须配置如 `pytest-timeout` 在 60s 内不吐出新用例则强制转态输出挂起栈。 |
